thread.title: BRIEF-Hemfosa Rental Income Amounted To MSEK 792 In Q4

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Hemfosa Rental Income Amounted To MSEK 792 In Q4
text:
Feb 16 (Reuters) - HEMFOSA:
* RENTAL INCOME AMOUNTED TO MSEK 792 (684) IN Q4 * BOARD PROPOSES A DIVIDEND FOR 2017 OF SEK 4.80 PER ORDINARY SHARE WITH QUARTERLY PAYMENT OF SEK 1.20 PER SHARE
* BOARD PROPOSES A DIVIDEND FOR 2017 OF SEK 10.00 PER PREFERENCE SHARE WITH QUARTERLY PAYMENT OF SEK 2.50 PER SHARE
* Q4 PROFIT FROM PROPERTY MANAGEMENT SEK 525 MILLION VERSUS SEK 537 MILLION YEAR AGO Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
